{"tha-ap26:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap26:0.2":"Subhutivagga ","tha-ap26:0.3":"Pancasilasamadaniyattheraapadana ","tha-ap26:1.1":"“Nagare candavatiya, ","tha-ap26:1.2":"bhatako asaham tada; ","tha-ap26:1.3":"Parakammayane yutto, ","tha-ap26:1.4":"pabbajjam na labhamaham. ","tha-ap26:2.1":"Mahandhakarapihita, ","tha-ap26:2.2":"tividhaggihi dayhare; ","tha-ap26:2.3":"Kena nu kho upayena, ","tha-ap26:2.4":"visamyutto bhave aham. ","tha-ap26:3.1":"Deyyadhammo ca me natthi, ","tha-ap26:3.2":"varako bhatako aham; ","tha-ap26:3.3":"Yannunaham pancasilam, ","tha-ap26:3.4":"rakkheyyam paripurayam. ","tha-ap26:4.1":"Anomadassissa munino, ","tha-ap26:4.2":"nisabho nama savako; ","tha-ap26:4.3":"Tamaham upasankamma, ","tha-ap26:4.4":"pancasikkhapadaggahim. ","tha-ap26:5.1":"Vassasatasahassani, ","tha-ap26:5.2":"ayu vijjati tavade; ","tha-ap26:5.3":"Tavata pancasilani, ","tha-ap26:5.4":"paripunnani gopayim. ","tha-ap26:6.1":"Maccukale ca sampatte, ","tha-ap26:6.2":"deva assasayanti mam; ","tha-ap26:6.3":"‘Ratho sahassayutto te, ","tha-ap26:6.4":"marisayam upatthito’. ","tha-ap26:7.1":"Vattante carime citte, ","tha-ap26:7.2":"mama silam anussarim; ","tha-ap26:7.3":"Tena kammena sukatena, ","tha-ap26:7.4":"tavatimsam agacchaham. ","tha-ap26:8.1":"Timsakkhattunca devindo, ","tha-ap26:8.2":"devarajjamakarayim; ","tha-ap26:8.3":"Dibbasukham anubhavim, ","tha-ap26:8.4":"accharahi purakkhato. ","tha-ap26:9.1":"Pancasattatikkhattunca, ","tha-ap26:9.2":"cakkavatti ahosaham; ","tha-ap26:9.3":"Padesarajjam vipulam, ","tha-ap26:9.4":"gananato asankhiyam. ","tha-ap26:10.1":"Devaloka cavitvana, ","tha-ap26:10.2":"sukkamulena codito; ","tha-ap26:10.3":"Pure vesaliyam jato, ","tha-ap26:10.4":"mahasale suaddhake. ","tha-ap26:11.1":"Vassupanayike kale, ","tha-ap26:11.2":"dippante jinasasane; ","tha-ap26:11.3":"Mata ca me pita ceva, ","tha-ap26:11.4":"pancasikkhapadaggahum. ","tha-ap26:12.1":"Saha sutvanaham silam, ","tha-ap26:12.2":"mama silam anussarim; ","tha-ap26:12.3":"Ekasane nisiditva, ","tha-ap26:12.4":"arahattamapapunim. ","tha-ap26:13.1":"<b>Jatiya pancavassena</b>, ","tha-ap26:13.2":"arahattamapapunim; ","tha-ap26:13.3":"Upasampadayi buddho, ","tha-ap26:13.4":"gunamannaya cakkhuma. ","tha-ap26:14.1":"Paripunnani gopetva, ","tha-ap26:14.2":"pancasikkhapadanaham; ","tha-ap26:14.3":"Aparimeyye ito kappe, ","tha-ap26:14.4":"vinipatam na gacchaham. ","tha-ap26:15.1":"Svaham yasamanubhavim, ","tha-ap26:15.2":"tesam silana vahasa; ","tha-ap26:15.3":"Kappakotimpi kittento, ","tha-ap26:15.4":"kittaye ekadesakam. ","tha-ap26:16.1":"Panca silani gopetva, ","tha-ap26:16.2":"tayo hetu labhamaham; ","tha-ap26:16.3":"Dighayuko mahabhogo, ","tha-ap26:16.4":"tikkhapanno bhavamaham. ","tha-ap26:17.1":"Sankittento ca sabbesam, ","tha-ap26:17.2":"adhimattanca porisam; ","tha-ap26:17.3":"Bhavabhave samsaritva, ","tha-ap26:17.4":"ete thane labhamaham. ","tha-ap26:18.1":"Aparimeyyasilesu, ","tha-ap26:18.2":"vattanta jinasavaka; ","tha-ap26:18.3":"Bhavesu yadi rajjeyyum, ","tha-ap26:18.4":"vipako kidiso bhave. ","tha-ap26:19.1":"Sucinnam me pancasilam, ","tha-ap26:19.2":"bhatakena tapassina; ","tha-ap26:19.3":"Tena silenaham ajja, ","tha-ap26:19.4":"mocayim sabbabandhana. ","tha-ap26:20.1":"Aparimeyye ito kappe, ","tha-ap26:20.2":"panca silani gopayim; ","tha-ap26:20.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap26:20.4":"pancasilanidam phalam. ","tha-ap26:21.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap26:21.2":"vimokkhapi ca atthime; ","tha-ap26:21.3":"Chalabhinna sacchikata, ","tha-ap26:21.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap26:22.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma pancasilasamadaniyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap26:23.1":"Pancasilasamadaniyattherassapadanam catuttham. "}